 🔧 Create .env.example File

```env
	Database Configuration
POSTGRES_USER=postgres
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=postgres
POSTGRES_DB=todo_db
POSTGRES_HOST=postgres
POSTGRES_PORT=5432

	Redis Configuration
REDIS_HOST=redis
REDIS_PORT=6379

	Application Configuration
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=5000

	Frontend URL (for CORS)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
